config BR2_PACKAGE_DRDR_INIT
	bool "drdr-init (DrDrOS PID 1)"
	help
	  drdr-init is DrDrOS's custom PID 1. It mounts /proc, /sys, /dev,
	  paints the framebuffer splash, then exec()s the shell. Replaces
	  BusyBox init when BR2_INIT_NONE=y.

	  Cross-compiled from the workspace at $(BR2_EXTERNAL_DRDROS_PATH)/../..
	  using the host's rustup toolchain (target x86_64-unknown-linux-musl).
	  Buildroot's musl is not used — the rustup target ships its own.

	  https://github.com/gravijet/DrDrOS
